Speaking for my own class <br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>Paladin - keep a number of grouped people alive, (wave of prexus LoH ect) while outputing a certain DPS<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
