This actually works, but it only looks at about 1/5th of what we can actually do, and it doesnt look at our traditional group/raid roles.<br>
<br>
Raid wise we are some of the best offtank/addtanks in the game. We do well in the 'watch and heal the group role, but it reduces our dps to nothing. We are one of the top classes vs ae's as well. We can sometimes act as main healers of a group, but i have no plans on purposefully recreating the paladin, pulling monk, pulling monk, mage, warrior situation again. <br>
